<mxCell id="n2" value="Build → Flash → Boot → Verify — the AX7101 pipeline" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;fontSize=22;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=6;fontColor=#212121;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="20" width="1200" height="34" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
<mxCell id="n3" value="1 · BUILD   —   dev host · Vivado

$ sw/litex/build.sh ax7101
  mandatory: --coherent-dma
  --gtx-tx-invert --all-blocks
$ --with-spiflash --flashboot full
    → pins BITSTREAM COMPRESS
  3×32-thread seed sweep
  GATE: WNS ≥ 0" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#E8F5E9;strokeColor=#2E7D32;fontSize=13;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=6;fontColor=#212121;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="150" width="440" height="332" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
<mxCell id="n4" value="OUTPUT
compressed .bit ~1.74 MiB (60% off 3.65)
+ kernel · dtb · rootfs · opensbi" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#2E7D32;fontSize=12;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=6;fontColor=#212121;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="504" width="440" height="64" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
<mxCell id="n5" value="2 · FLASH   —   JTAG → QSPI (16 MB)

$ deploy.sh flash  (bitstream @0)
$ deploy.sh flash-images
    matched set, FBI-wrapped
    per-slot budget + --verify
  openFPGALoader -c ft232
  RULE: flash the WHOLE set —
  a gateware-only load won&#x27;t boot" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF3E0;strokeColor=#EF6C00;fontSize=13;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=6;fontColor=#212121;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="534" y="150" width="440" height="332" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
<mxCell id="n6" value="OUTPUT
persistent QSPI image:
bitstream@0 · kernel · dtb · rootfs" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#EF6C00;fontSize=12;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=6;fontColor=#212121;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="534" y="504" width="440" height="64" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
<mxCell id="n7" value="3 · BOOT   —   on target · self-configures

$ power on / power-cycle
  FPGA config-boots from QSPI
  LiteX BIOS → DDR3 init
  linux_flashboot QSPI→DRAM
  OpenSBI (M-mode) → Linux
  S50milan provisions CSRs
  ptp4l · phc2sys · linkmon up" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#E3F2FD;strokeColor=#1565C0;fontSize=13;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=6;fontColor=#212121;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1028" y="150" width="440" height="332" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
<mxCell id="n8" value="OUTPUT
buildroot Linux on VexiiRiscv,
Milan NIC live" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#1565C0;fontSize=12;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=6;fontColor=#212121;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1028" y="504" width="440" height="64" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
<mxCell id="n9" value="4 · VERIFY   —   on the bench

$ devmem 0x90000000 == &#x27;MILN&#x27;
    (M-A2 first-silicon smoke)
  link up · GM / talker / listener
$ CERT 63/63
  behave · TB · audio E2E
  REGISTER_MAP.md = the ABI
  BENCH_TOPOLOGY.md = the rig" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F3E5F5;strokeColor=#6A1B9A;fontSize=13;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=6;fontColor=#212121;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1522" y="150" width="440" height="332" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
